snippet.title: [Quake] Soul of Evil: Indian Summer - Map06 "Summer's End" NM 100%
snippet.description:
gremlins steal your guns, dragons instakill you. there's so much to love in this set of levels but so much to loathe too! i am thoroughly convinced that the bane boss in map05 is flat out impossible on nightmare difficulty without some horrible tricks.

recorded with quakespasm 0.93. download indian summer here: https://www.quaddicted.com/reviews/nsoe2.html
